703727f-a.title: Brooklyn: Columbia Street - Congress Street
703727f-a.text:
6d-76 Columbia Street, west side, north from Warren to Congress Streets.
A1so shown, is Warren Street, north side, east of Columbia Street; The
buildings under demolition at the N.W. corner, are numbered respectively from
left to right, Noa. 76 and 74.
March 27, 1937.
P. L. Sperm.
NOREPPODUCTIONS.
